5000|$|John Cossette {{became the}} {{producer}} of <b>the</b> <b>Grammy</b> Awards following <b>the</b> departure of his father from the awards show. Cossette remained involved with the television broadcast of <b>the</b> <b>Grammy</b> Awards {{for more than twenty}} years, and also produced <b>the</b> Latin <b>Grammy</b> Awards show and <b>the</b> <b>Grammy</b> nominations concert. Most recently, Cossette worked as the executive producer of <b>the</b> 53rd <b>Grammy</b> Awards held on February 13, 2011.|$|R
