25|$|Muse {{have won}} {{numerous}} awards, including two Grammy Awards, winning <b>the</b> <b>Grammys</b> for Best Rock Album for The Resistance and Drones, two Brit Awards, winning Best British Live Act twice, five MTV Europe Music Awards and eight NME Awards. They have sold over 20 million albums worldwide.|$|E
